SOUTH CAROLINA
Pickens County

Galax aphylla L.

Rich mafic slope near the headwaters of Eastatoe Creek off
Hwy 178. Species include tulip poplar, red maple, black
locust, sourwood, few hemlocks, witch hazel, trillium spp.,
blue cohash, red buckeye and magnolia.
